.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/08/1</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 08:11:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-08 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/08/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F44639bd0ea260137cfba005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“It’s worse than I first suspected, Mr. Binkley—you
 don’t even have a funny bone.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/08/0</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 08:10:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-07 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/07/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fcaf57e60d7410137c8a6005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Early physics&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/07/4</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 08:09:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-07 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/07/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F590c4ea0df110137cbaf005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“So, Carl—attacked by any giant carrots lately?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/07/3</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 08:08:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>T